  "article": "In a bold move to address the global e-waste epidemic, Samsung has unveiled the Upcycle Promise, a revolutionary program that aims to breathe new life into discarded electronics. This innovative initiative represents a significant step forward in the company's commitment to sustainability and environmental responsibility.

