At the heart of the Upcycle Promise is a state-of-the-art upcycling facility, where Samsung's team of engineers and designers work tirelessly to identify the hidden potential in discarded devices. Through a meticulous process of disassembly, component analysis, and innovative repurposing, they are able to extract and repurpose a wide range of materials, from precious metals to high-performance plastics.

