As the world grapples with the growing e-waste crisis, the Upcycle Promise stands as a shining example of how technology can be leveraged to drive positive change. By pioneering this groundbreaking initiative, Samsung is not only setting a new benchmark for sustainability but also paving the way for a more circular economy, where the lifecycle of electronic devices is extended and their impact on the environment is minimized.

