  "article": "The Dow Jones Industrial Average plummeted over 700 points on Thursday, as investors reacted with alarm to President Trump's announcement of new global tariffs. The sell-off ramped up throughout the trading session, with the S&P 500 and Nasdaq Composite also posting significant losses.

